# The API image consumes only the explicit inputs copied by Dockerfile.
# Keep the Fly build context small and make additions deliberate: a new COPY
# source must be allow-listed here in the same change.
**

!Dockerfile
!package.json
!bun.lock
!tsconfig.json

!src/
!src/**

# bin/deploy.sh creates these immediately before `fly deploy` and removes
# them afterwards. They carry the canonical registry/library/doctrine bytes.
!agenttool.jsonld.bundled
!kingdom-bundle.json.bundled
!doctrine-docs.bundled/
!doctrine-docs.bundled/**
